snippet.title: NCF-248 Data Forensics and Cyber Education
snippet.description: On today's show, our host Abe Thompson talks with Amber Schroader on the world of data forensics and the impotence of having more women in cybersecurity. In an age of continuously generated data and diminishing privacy, it's essential to educate ourselves on where our information goes. As a prominent female in the cyber industry, Amber Schroader has done a lot for educating the next generation of women in cyber, whether for personal online safety or as a full-on career. Listen in as we discuss creating the future of women in cybersecurity on NCF.
